libprojectM
------------------------------------------
projectM is an OpenGL based advanced music visualization program for 
Linux, Mac OSX, and Windows. It is backward compatible with all the 
features of Milkdrop 1.x, but has many new toys and enhancements.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-50
  libgcc1-4.3.2-2
  libGL1-7.4.4-1
  libstdc++6-4.3.2-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.19.51-1
  cmake-2.6.4-10
  cygport-0.9.7-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.2-2
  gcc4-g++-4.3.2-2
  make-3.81-2

Canonical website:
  http://projectm.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/projectm/files/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack libprojectM-1.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./libprojectM-1.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libprojectM-1.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libprojectM-common-1.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libprojectM-devel-1.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libprojectM2-1.2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

